DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       _X_r_o_a_c_h  displays  disgusting cockroaches on your root win-
       dow. These creapy crawlies scamper around until they  find
       a  window  to  hide  under. Whenever you move or iconify a
       window, the exposed beetles again scamper for cover.

